Package org.jsonurl.text

Provides interfaces and base support for generating JSON→URL text.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonStringBuilder
    A JsonTextBuilder that builds a string.
    JsonTextAppendable<A,R>
    A JsonTextBuilder that is also Appendable.
    JsonTextBuilder<R>
    A thing that can serialize the JSON→URL data model.
    NumberText
    NumberText provides access to a parsed JSON→URL number literal.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsonUrlStringBuilder
    A JsonUrlTextAppender that appends JSON→URL text to a StringBuilder.
    JsonUrlTextAppender<A extends Appendable,R>
    A JsonTextAppendable that appends JSON→URL text to any Appendable.
    NumberBuilder
    A NumberBuilder implements the builder pattern for JSON→URL number literals.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NumberText.Exponent
    type of parsed exponent string.
